==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Prizer
<hw>Priz"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See 3d
<er>Prize</er>.]</ety> <def>One who estimates or sets the value of a
thing; an appraiser.</def> <rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Prizer</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Prizer
<hw>Priz"er</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See 1st <er>Prize</er>.]</ety>
<def>One who contends for a prize; a prize fighter; a challenger.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Appeareth no man yet to answer the <qex>prizer</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>B. Jonson.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Prizing</ent>⟦br⟧
